subdefinitions.definition: A number of places in England : A village and civil parish in Teignbridge district, Devon , England ( OS grid ref SX9583 ) . A suburban area in the borough of Brent and borough of Harrow , Greater London ; Kenton Road forms the boundary between boroughs ( OS grid ref TQ1788 ) . A village and civil parish in Mid Suffolk district, Suffolk ( OS grid ref TM1965 ) . A suburb in the Metropolitan Borough of Newcastle upon Tyne , Tyne and Wear ( OS grid ref NZ2267 ) .

A number of places in the United States : A town in Kent County , Delaware . An unincorporated community in Houghton County , Michigan . A city , the county seat of Hardin County , Ohio . A census-designated place in Cimarron County , Oklahoma . A town in Gibson County , Tennessee .

definitions.definition: A habitational surname from Old English .
A male given name transferred from the surname .
